9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1225, L.D. 1830, “Resolve, to Establish
10 a Pilot Program to Protect Firefighters from Cancer”
11 Amend the resolve by striking out the title and substituting the following:
12 'Resolve, to Expand the Recipients of the Report on the Public Safety Health and
13 Wellness Grant Pilot Program and Authorize Legislation to Be Submitted in
14 Response to the Report'
15 Amend the resolve by striking out everything after the title and inserting the following:
16 'Sec. 1. Report on public safety health and wellness grant pilot program.
17 Resolved: That the Department of Public Safety shall submit the report required by Public
18 Law 2023, chapter 643, Part T, section 5 no later than January 10, 2026 to the Joint
19 Standing Committee on Health Coverage, Insurance and Financial Services in addition to
20 the Joint Standing Committee on Health and Human Services and the Joint Standing
21 Committee on Criminal Justice and Public Safety as required by Public Law 2023, chapter
22 643, Part T, section 5. After reviewing the report, the Joint Standing Committee on Health
23 and Human Services, the Joint Standing Committee on Health Coverage, Insurance and
24 Financial Services or the Joint Standing Committee on Criminal Justice and Public Safety
25 may report out legislation to the Second Regular Session of the 132nd Legislature.'
26 Amend the resolve by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or
27 section number to read consecutively.
28 SUMMARY
2299 This amendment replaces the resolve and changes the title. The amendment directs the
3300 Department of Public Safety to submit the report on the public safety health and wellness
3311 grant pilot program required to be completed no later than January 10, 2026 pursuant to
3322 Public Law 2023, chapter 643, Part T, section 5 to the Joint Standing Committee on Health
3333 Coverage, Insurance and Financial Services. The amendment also authorizes the Joint
3344 Standing Committee on Health Coverage, Insurance and Financial Services, the Joint
3355 Standing Committee on Health and Human Services or the Joint Standing Committee on
